Package se.kvirkel.tankwars.network

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TWNetwork
    network class, registers and contains the classes we want to send over the network
    TWNetwork.TWEntityContainer
    Synchronized entity list containing the entities and methods for returning different items in the list
    TWNetwork.TWMap
    the game map to be played
    TWNetwork.TWMessageContainer
    Message container, used by the chat.
    TWNetwork.TWPlayerStatus
    PlayerStatus that is sent over network
    TWNetworkClient
    The clientside network handler: sends messages to the server and processes messages when received.
    TWNetworkServer
    the network server handling the connection between gameserver and network client.
